<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Tejas</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: #2c3e50; /* Dark background */
        color: #fff;
      }

      .container {
        width: 85%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #34495e;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .navbar {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        width: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9b59b6, #3498db); /* Vibrant gradient */
        color: white;
        padding: 15px 0;
        z-index: 1000;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      }

      .navbar .logo {
        font-size: 2.4rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #f8d210;
        margin-left: 20px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      }

      .navbar ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        text-align: right;
      }

      .navbar ul li {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-right: 20px;
      }

      .navbar ul li a {
        color: #f8d210;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
        text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      }

      .navbar ul li a:hover {
        color: #fff;
        text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
      }

      .main-section {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00c6ff, #0072ff);
        padding: 40px;
        margin-top: 80px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00c6ff, #0072ff);
        color: #fff;
      }

      .main-section h1 {
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      }

      .main-section p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #f1f1f1;
        line-height: 1.8;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      .features-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 20px;
        list-style-type: none;
      }

      .features-list li {
        flex: 1 1 calc(30% - 20px);
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffb74d, #ff9800);
        color: #fff;
      }

      .features-list h2 {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .features-list p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .feedback-section {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff79c6, #f50057); /* Bright pink gradient */
        padding: 40px 20px;
        margin-top: 40px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        color: #fff;
      }

      .feedback-section h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .feedback-form {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .feedback-form label {
        font-weight: bold;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #333;
      }

      .feedback-form input,
      .feedback-form textarea {
        width: calc(100% - 20px);
        padding: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .feedback-form textarea {
        resize: vertical;
        min-height: 100px;
      }

      .feedback-form button {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6f61, #ff9f5f); /* Gradient button */
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 1rem;
        transition: background 0.3s ease;
      }

      .feedback-form button:hover {
        background: #ff5722;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .container {
          width: 90%;
        }

        .features-list {
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 20px;
        }

        .features-list li {
          flex: 1;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav class="navbar">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="logo">Tejas</span>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/register">Register</a></li>
          <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about-us">About Us</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="main-section">
        <h1>Tejas Sports Management System</h1>
        <p>
          Welcome to Tejas, your sports management platform designed to enhance your
          sports experience.
        </p>

        <ul class="features-list">
          <li>
            <h2>Team Management</h2>
            <p>
              Create and manage teams for various sports activities. Assign
              players, update team details, and view team statistics.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2>Schedule Management</h2>
            <p>
              View and manage upcoming sports events, matches, and sessions.
              Filter by sport, date, and venue.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2>Player Registration</h2>
            <p>
              Players can register, update their profiles, and manage their
              participation in sports events.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2>Statistics and Reports</h2>
            <p>
              Generate reports on team performance, player statistics, and
              overall participation. Analyze trends and make data-driven
              decisions.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2>Notifications and Alerts</h2>
            <p>
              Receive notifications about schedule changes, upcoming events, and
              important announcements in real-time.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2>Administration Panel</h2>
            <p>
              Administrators have access to a dedicated dashboard to manage
              users, teams, sessions, and system settings.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="feedback-section">
        <h2>Feedback</h2>
        <div class="feedback-form">
          <form action="/submit-feedback" method="POST">
            <label for="name">Name:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required />

            <label for="email">Email:</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required />

            <label for="message">Message:</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea>

            <button type="submit">Submit Feedback</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
